{"tid":1940570,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"逾百人白色情人節參與Studio 9私人派對　有四人確診","createTime":"2020-03-24T00:37:51.000Z","updateTime":"2020-03-24T04:21:48.000Z","uid":72009,"like":7,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":11,"replies":[{"pid":"6bf62025800ead2e36ca460e863ff9ade6ea6502","tid":1940570,"uid":72009,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-24T00:37:51.000Z","msg":"本港今日（23日）新增39宗確診新型冠狀病毒肺炎（俗稱武漢肺炎）個案，情況令人擔憂。香港衛生防護中心傳染病處主任張竹君表示，早前公布的四宗個案，則第169、208、277及315曾同日到過黃竹坑聯合工業大廈9樓，在3月14日（白色情人節）於Studio 9參與一場逾百人參與的私人派對。<br />\n<br />\n張竹君表示，除了第277宗個案27歲女子，其餘三人是結伴參與該場派對，認為不一定是在派對中受感染，但指參與任何形式的派對，若沒有佩帶口罩，均有機會構成傳播風險，已聯絡派對主辦人，向曾參與派對的人士發消息，有需要聯絡衛生防護中心。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.hk01.com/%E7%A4%BE%E6%9C%83%E6%96%B0%E8%81%9E/451582/%E6%96%B0%E5%86%A0%E8%82%BA%E7%82%8E-%E9%80%BE%E7%99%BE%E4%BA%BA%E7%99%BD%E8%89%B2%E6%83%85%E4%BA%BA%E7%AF%80%E5%8F%83%E8%88%87studio-9%E7%A7%81%E4%BA%BA%E6%B4%BE%E5%B0%8D-%E6%9C%89%E5%9B%9B%E4%BA%BA%E7%A2%BA%E8%A8%BA\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.hk01.com%2F%25E7%25A4%25BE%25E6%259C%2583%25E6%2596%25B0%25E8%2581%259E%2F451582%2F%25E6%2596%25B0%25E5%2586%25A0%25E8%2582%25BA%25E7%2582%258E-%25E9%2580%25BE%25E7%2599%25BE%25E4%25BA%25BA%25E7%2599%25BD%25E8%2589%25B2%25E6%2583%2585%25E4%25BA%25BA%25E7%25AF%2580%25E5%258F%2583%25E8%2588%2587studio-9%25E7%25A7%2581%25E4%25BA%25BA%25E6%25B4%25BE%25E5%25B0%258D-%25E6%259C%2589%25E5%259B%259B%25E4%25BA%25BA%25E7%25A2%25BA%25E8%25A8%25BA&d=%2BQAufOe15lwSrakhKFXs1s2proQWM4oxojYLcFbEfDU%3D&h=e02994f7\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.hk01.com/%E7%A4%BE%E6%9C%83%E6%96%B0%E8%81%9E/451582/%E6%96%B0%E5%86%A0%E8%82%BA%E7%82%8E-%E9%80%BE%E7%99%BE%E4%BA%BA%E7%99%BD%E8%89%B2%E6%83%85%E4%BA%BA%E7%AF%80%E5%8F%83%E8%88%87studio-9%E7%A7%81%E4%BA%BA%E6%B4%BE%E5%B0%8D-%E6%9C%89%E5%9B%9B%E4%BA%BA%E7%A2%BA%E8%A8%BA</a><br />\n<br />\n群p，不停體液交換<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3954887706784b41dfd6c395fae1e64f2734a942","tid":1940570,"uid":35746,"